sources-for-2015-categorized-expert-tips/">des ressources pour WordPress </a>pour lancer l&rsquo;ann&eacute;e 2015, c&rsquo;est ici que vous pouvez commenc&eacute; ! (en)</p>\n<h3>Thierry est pass&eacute; &agrave; la Marmite</h3>\n<p>Pour son 9e Podcast Alex de WPMarmite interroge <a href="http://wpmarmite.com/pat-episode-009/">Thierry Pigot</a>.</p>\n<h3>Pourquoi utiliser Mailchimp ?</h3>\n<p><a href="http://wpformation.com/pourquoi-utiliser-le-plugin-mailchimp-avec-wordpress/">C&rsquo;est la question que se pose S&eacute;bastien Pierrepack </a>sur WPFormation.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=OpwsDWuoAxw:VjMKP94_UKk:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/OpwsDWuoAxw" height="1" width="1" alt="">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:10;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:70:"WP Formation : Po